{"schemaVersion":{"major":0,"minor":3,"patch":0},"primaryContentSections":[{"declarations":[{"tokens":[{"kind":"keyword","text":"func"},{"kind":"text","text":" "},{"text":"launch","kind":"identifier"},{"kind":"text","text":"("},{"kind":"externalParam","text":"files"},{"text":": ","kind":"text"},{"text":"ListRef","kind":"typeIdentifier","preciseIdentifier":"s:4GLib7ListRefV"},{"text":"? = nil, ","kind":"text"},{"text":"context","kind":"externalParam"},{"kind":"text","text":": "},{"text":"AppLaunchContextRef","kind":"typeIdentifier","preciseIdentifier":"s:3GIO19AppLaunchContextRefV","identifier":"doc:\/\/GIO\/documentation\/GIO\/AppLaunchContextRef"},{"text":"? = nil) ","kind":"text"},{"kind":"keyword","text":"throws"},{"kind":"text","text":" -> "},{"kind":"typeIdentifier","text":"Bool","preciseIdentifier":"s:Sb"}],"languages":["swift"],"platforms":["macOS"]}],"kind":"declarations"},{"kind":"content","content":[{"anchor":"discussion","level":2,"text":"Discussion","type":"heading"},{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"text":"To launch the application without arguments pass a ","type":"text"},{"code":"NULL","type":"codeVoice"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"code":"files","type":"codeVoice"},{"type":"text","text":" list."}]},{"inlineContent":[{"text":"Note that even if the launch is successful the application launched","type":"text"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"text":"can fail to start if it runs into problems during startup. There is","type":"text"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"text":"no way to detect this.","type":"text"}],"type":"paragraph"},{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"Some URIs can be changed when passed through a GFile (for instance"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"unsupported URIs with strange formats like mailto:), so if you have"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"a textual URI you want to pass in as argument, consider using"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"[method"},{"code":"Gio.AppInfo.launch_uris","type":"codeVoice"},{"text":"] instead.","type":"text"}]},{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"text":"The launched application inherits the environment of the launching","type":"text"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"process, but it can be modified with [method"},{"code":"Gio.AppLaunchContext.setenv","type":"codeVoice"},{"text":"]","type":"text"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"text":"and [method","type":"text"},{"code":"Gio.AppLaunchContext.unsetenv","type":"codeVoice"},{"type":"text","text":"]."}]},{"inlineContent":[{"text":"On UNIX, this function sets the ","type":"text"},{"code":"GIO_LAUNCHED_DESKTOP_FILE","type":"codeVoice"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"type":"text","text":"environment variable with the path of the launched desktop file and"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"code":"GIO_LAUNCHED_DESKTOP_FILE_PID","type":"codeVoice"},{"text":" to the process id of the launched","type":"text"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"process. This can be used to ignore "},{"code":"GIO_LAUNCHED_DESKTOP_FILE","type":"codeVoice"},{"type":"text","text":","},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"should it be inherited by further processes. The "},{"code":"DISPLAY","type":"codeVoice"},{"text":",","type":"text"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"code":"XDG_ACTIVATION_TOKEN","type":"codeVoice"},{"type":"text","text":" and "},{"code":"DESKTOP_STARTUP_ID","type":"codeVoice"},{"type":"text","text":" environment"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"type":"text","text":"variables are also set, based on information provided in "},{"code":"context","type":"codeVoice"},{"type":"text","text":"."}],"type":"paragraph"}]}],"variants":[{"paths":["\/documentation\/gio\/osxappinforef\/launch(files:context:)"],"traits":[{"interfaceLanguage":"swift"}]}],"kind":"symbol","identifier":{"url":"doc:\/\/GIO\/documentation\/GIO\/OsxAppInfoRef\/launch(files:context:)","interfaceLanguage":"swift"},"sections":[],"abstract":[{"type":"text","text":"Launches the application. Passes "},{"type":"codeVoice","code":"files"},{"type":"text","text":" to the launched application"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"as arguments, using the optional "},{"code":"context","type":"codeVoice"},{"text":" to get information","type":"text"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"type":"text","text":"about the details of the launcher (like what screen it is on)."},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"text":"On error, ","type":"text"},{"type":"codeVoice","code":"error"},{"type":"text","text":" will be set accordingly."}],"hierarchy":{"paths":[["doc:\/\/GIO\/documentation\/GIO","doc:\/\/GIO\/documentation\/GIO\/OsxAppInfoRef","doc:\/\/GIO\/documentation\/GIO\/OsxAppInfoRef\/AppInfoProtocol-Implementations"]]},"metadata":{"title":"launch(files:context:)","extendedModule":"GIO","externalID":"s:3GIO15AppInfoProtocolPAAE6launch5files7contextSb4GLib7ListRefVSg_AA0b13LaunchContextJ0VSgtKF::SYNTHESIZED::s:3GIO13OsxAppInfoRefV","role":"symbol","roleHeading":"Instance Method","symbolKind":"method","fragments":[{"kind":"keyword","text":"func"},{"kind":"text","text":" "},{"text":"launch","kind":"identifier"},{"kind":"text","text":"("},{"kind":"externalParam","text":"files"},{"text":": ","kind":"text"},{"text":"ListRef","kind":"typeIdentifier","preciseIdentifier":"s:4GLib7ListRefV"},{"kind":"text","text":"?, "},{"kind":"externalParam","text":"context"},{"text":": ","kind":"text"},{"text":"AppLaunchContextRef","kind":"typeIdentifier","preciseIdentifier":"s:3GIO19AppLaunchContextRefV"},{"text":"?) ","kind":"text"},{"text":"throws","kind":"keyword"},{"text":" -> ","kind":"text"},{"kind":"typeIdentifier","preciseIdentifier":"s:Sb","text":"Bool"}],"modules":[{"name":"GIO"}]},"references":{"doc://GIO/documentation/GIO/OsxAppInfoProtocol":{"kind":"symbol","role":"symbol","identifier":"doc:\/\/GIO\/documentation\/GIO\/OsxAppInfoProtocol","abstract":[{"text":"The ","type":"text"},{"type":"reference","isActive":true,"identifier":"doc:\/\/GIO\/documentation\/GI